OL,3,CGuernsey States spent #44 million more
OL,4,Cthan it brought in during 2024
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey spent #44
OL,7,Fmillion more on core day-to-day
OL,8,Factivities such as running public
OL,9,Fservices and benefits than it made
OL,10,Fthrough income last year.
OL,12,FThat overspend includes a #22 million
OL,13,Fdeficit in non-infrastructure projects
OL,14,Fsuch as IT changes and a #13 million
OL,15,Fdeficit in social security funds.
OL,17,FIn better news, States' investments
OL,18,Fwere collectively #130 million more
OL,19,Fvaluable at the end of 2024 than 2023.
