OL,6,FHowever, this is a valuation rather
OL,7,Fthan a guaranteed return and the funds
OL,8,Fremain invested in a portfolio that
OL,9,Fregularly changes value.
OL,11,FOverall, the States ongoing financial
OL,12,Fposition is an underlying annual
OL,13,Fdeficit of around #56 million.
