OL,3,CGuernsey States spent #44 million more
OL,4,Cthan it brought in during 2024
OL,6,FThe outgoing Vice President of Policy
OL,7,Fand Resources, Deputy Heidi Soulsby,
OL,8,Fadds: "We are not raising enough
OL,9,Fthrough taxes to fund the services our
OL,10,Fcommunity relies on.
OL,12,F"The value of investments is of course
OL,13,Fimportant ... but they don't impact
OL,14,Fthe amount of money we have available
OL,15,Fto deliver public services and invest
OL,16,Fin much-needed infrastructure.
OL,18,F"The decision for the next States will
OL,19,Fnot be whether something needs to be
OL,20,Fdone, but what should be done to
OL,21,Fbalance the books."
